ofiles.wordpress.org/hikingyogi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/24279a3e94952c5c66db5abf3a155a37572941b94d9e29549d9f95f9012e704d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/24279a3e94952c5c66db5abf3a155a37572941b94d9e29549d9f95f9012e704d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hikingyogi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hikingyogi</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 25, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have been in IT for 30 years, but I have ZERO experience in designing web sites. I allowed AI to develop my initial site and then edited it to suit my style and needs. However, when I got to the products page, I was totally stuck on how to display our products by category. I researched it and tried to follow all of the instructions but because I have a block design, some of the things that were mentioned were not in the right place or didn\'t exist at all. Over the span of 3 days and multiple people, the members of the forum checked out my site and carefully explained what I would need to do. The final person who helped me even sent a video, which was extremely helpful. I can\'t thank everyone enough for the assistance - even when it felt hopeless, they stuck with me and got it taken care of.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:227:\"Tout ce dont vous avez besoin pour crer une boutique en ligne en quelques jours et la faire prosprer des annes. Woo vous accompagne, de votre toute premire vente au dveloppement colossal de votre chiffre daffaires.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.10.3.6.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.png